interesting points: The object was reported to be faster than any jet,The sighting lasted for 6 minutes,The object was described to be cocooned in a bright light,The object may have been a retrograde satellite,The report includes details about potential subsequent investigations.
sighted object: an unusual object traveling at high speed
witness description: the report was submitted by an individual who observed the object
